<p>The Security Advisory Committee is designed to provide a quarterly forum for Downtown Visions and the Wilmington Police Department to meet with security personnel from businesses and organizations located in the BID to share information, discuss current crime trends and express common concerns. The goal of the Security Advisory Committee is to develop creative, unified strategies to aid the Wilmington Police Department in achieving their goal of making downtown Wilmington as safe as possible.</p>]]></description></item><item><title>Cleaning Ambassadors</title><category>Initiatives</category><category>Cleaning</category><dc:creator>Sarah Zero</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 04 Aug 2015 20:02:54 +0000</pubDate><link>http://downtownwilmingtonde.com/initiatives-blog/2015/8/4/cleaning-ambassadors</link><guid isPermaLink="false">5515b9dfe4b0570dfe189823:55bffa25e4b0e6d1aa60cca1:55c11a60e4b09b2fcd06979b</guid><description><![CDATA[
	
	
		
			
				
